comment: Love (CLE) cleanly strips the ball from Green (GSW) prior to Green moving his pivot foot.
Love (CLE) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Green's (GSW) driving layup attempt.

Livingston (GSW) makes contact with James' (CLE) arm that affects his movement to the basket and layup attempt. The initial contact occurs prior to the slight movement of James' pivot foot on the spin move that can only be detected with slow motion.
Dellavedova (CLE) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Curry's (GSW) driving layup attempt.
Iguodala (GSW) makes incidental contact with James' (CLE) arm that does not affect his shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) and Dellavedova (CLE) make incidental contact with one another while jumping for the loose ball.
Dellavedova (CLE) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt and allows him to land.
Dellavedova (CLE) commits a take foul during rebounding against Iguodala (GSW).
Green's (GSW) left arm makes contact with James' (CLE) body that affects his ability to jump and layup attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Livingston (GSW) clamps Love's (CLE) arm affecting his ability to secure the rebound.
Thompson (CLE) clamps Iguodala's (GSW) arm, affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Iguodala (GSW) grabs Smith's (CLE) arm prior to the start of his upward shooting motion. The foul is incorrectly called on Livingston (GSW) and Smith should have only been awarded 2 FT attempts.
Dellavedova (CLE) commits a take foul during rebounding against Green (GSW).
